OL,3,CGuernsey's minimum wage to rise above
OL,4,CUK rate
OL,6,FGuernsey politicians have voted to
OL,7,Fincrease the adult minimum wage by 5%
OL,8,Fto #12.60 per hour.
OL,10,FThe change, which is set to come in
OL,11,Ffrom 1 October, will put the island in
OL,12,Fthe "middle of the pack" compared to
OL,13,Fits competitors, according to the
OL,14,FEmployment and Social Security
OL,15,FCommittee (ESS).
OL,17,FYounger workers will also get a pay
OL,18,Fboost, with 16 and 17-year-olds to
OL,19,Freceive at least #11.35 per hour -
OL,20,Fcurrently they can be paid #10.80.
