OL,3,CGuernsey's minimum wage to rise above
OL,4,CUK rate
OL,6,FHowever, Jersey still has a higher
OL,7,Fadult minimum wage at #13 per hour,
OL,8,Fwhich came into force at the start of
OL,9,FApril.
OL,11,FGuernsey's minimum wage currently sits
OL,12,Fat #12 per hour but the increase will
OL,13,Fsee it jump ahead of the UK, which
OL,14,Fstands at #12.21 an hour for those
OL,15,Faged 21 and over.
