OL,6,FSpeaking in the debate about the
OL,7,Fchanges, Peter Roffey, President of
OL,8,FESS, said: "I hope the new committee
OL,9,Fsticks to the timetable of getting
OL,10,Fthis increase through in October,
OL,11,Fgiving more time for employers to
OL,12,Fplan."
OL,14,FDeputy Roffey added that he personally
OL,15,Fwould have preferred raising the rate
OL,16,Ffurther to the same level as Jersey,
OL,17,Fbut the Committee decided otherwise.
