OL,6,FThe proposer of the amendment, Deputy
OL,7,FSasha Kazantseva-Miller, said in the
OL,8,Fdebate: "This move has come way too
OL,9,Fearly in my view. At the moment, we
OL,10,Fare in a period of uncertainty around
OL,11,Finflation trends.
OL,13,F"If inflation goes up, this proposal
OL,14,Fcould be unfair to the lowest-paid
OL,15,Fworkers.
OL,17,F"If the inflation goes down, we are
OL,18,Fproposing a disproportionately high
OL,19,Fincrease, which will have a
OL,20,Fsignificant effect on businesses and
OL,21,Fthe rest of the economy."
